msItem.note:
 (fols. 204r–207v and 216r–224r) Weekly canticles with titles,
                           marginal and interlinear gloss: 

(1) Confitebor tibi domine (Isaiah 12) (‘Canticum ysaie
                                 prophete’);

(2) Ego dixi (Isaiah 38: 10–21) (‘Canticum ezechie
                                 regis’);

(3) Exultauit cor meum (1 Samuel 2: 1–11) (‘Canticum anne
                                 prophetisse’);

(4) Cantemus domino (Exodus 15: 1–20) (‘Canticum moysi’);

(5) Domine audiui (Habakkuk 3) (‘Canticum abbacuc’);

(6) Avdite celi (Deuteronomy 32: 1–44) (‘canticum
                                 moysi’).
